com.cyc.baseclient.api

Class CompactHLIDConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyc.baseclient.api.CompactHLIDConverter

  • public class CompactHLIDConverter
extends Object
    A CFASL translating convert to/from compact external representations for CycL literal types (Strings and Numbers) without needing to access a Cyc image.
    See Also:
    DefaultCycObject.toCompactExternalId(Object, CycAccess), DefaultCycObject.fromCompactExternalId(String, CycAccess)
